text: Åke Hultberg (born 29 November 1949) is a Swedish equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:People from Västmanland County
